sources.title: Police Patrol (1933) MADGE BELLAMY
sources.description:
Stars: Madge Bellamy, Pat O'Malley, James Flavin
Director: Harry S. Webb

The constant battling over the same woman gets two detectives demoted to the toughest job in the Police Department--the Riot Squad. Madge Bellany (WHITE ZOMBIE) is the belle of the ball. (a.k.a. Riot Squad).
